      "writtenOn": "2017-04-24T14:44:20Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I think that this is fine, I don’t think we need to add anything to ScopedMmap to deal with protection on subranges. The Mprotect() that’s on there now is for convenience when dealing with the entire range. But…",
      "revId": "bf45ada33a432caf27bc795e6b55a10ca7cd9b70",
